The pay scales so decided will be approved and reviewed by Central Executive
Committee (CEC) periodically at least once in 3 years on the recommendation of the
General Secretary/President IIA.
The ‘Pay-Day’ for Executive and Non-executive staff will be 7th day of each month and
it will be followed in letter and spirit.
